                Step into the enchanting world of India’s rural folk tales, where stories from the vibrant North and lush South weave lessons of wisdom, courage, and community. From the golden fields of Punjab to the serene backwaters of Kerala, these narratives, passed down through generations, capture the heart of India’s diverse village cultures, filled with humor, spirituality, and timeless morals.
            </p>
